For more information about CFCC requirements for supported systems, see “Coupling facility and CFCC considerations” on page 281. Note: Parallel sysplex coupling and timing links connectivity for IBM z16 (M/T 3931) is supported to N-2 generation CPCs (IBM z16, IBM z15, and IBM z14).
